subject: R
object: So, Sally and Anne, let's start building the tracks. I count on you guys. Are you ready? Also, you need to play this game together, as both of you will see different views at all times. You can talk now to help each other. To see my instructions again, check the information icon on your screens. Time to play. Let's Go!
